object.property: SELECT TBSP_STATE , CASE WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'NORMAL' THEN '0' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'LOAD PENDING' THEN '1' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'LOAD IN PROGRESS' THEN '2' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'REORG IN PROGRESS' THEN '3' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'RESTORE IN PROGRESS' THEN '4' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'TABLE SPACE DELETION IN PROGRESS' THEN '5' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'TABLE SPACE CREATION IN PROGRESS' THEN '6' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'BACKUP IN PROGRESS' THEN '7' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'DMS REBALANCE IN PROGRESS' THEN '8' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'BACKUP PENDING' THEN '9' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'RESTORE PENDING' THEN '10' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'ROLL FORWARD PENDING' THEN '11' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'ROLL FORWARD IN PROGRESS' THEN '12' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'QUIESCED EXCLUSIVE' THEN '13' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'QUIESCED SHARE' THEN '14' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'QUIESCED UPDATE' THEN '15' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'STORAGE MAY BE DEFINED' THEN '16' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'STORAGE MUST BE DEFINED' THEN '17' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'DISABLE PENDING' THEN '18' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'DROP PENDING' THEN '19' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'SUSPEND WRITE' THEN '20' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'UNAVAILABLE' THEN '21' WHEN TBSP_STATE = 'OFFLINE AND NOT ACCESSIBLE' THEN '22' ELSE '21' END status, TBSP_UTILIZATION_PERCENT percentUsed, TBSP_TOTAL_SIZE_KB totalBytes, TBSP_USED_PAGES sizeUsed FROM SYSIBMADM.TBSP_UTILIZATION WHERE TBSP_NAME='${here/dbname}'

SELECT DB_STATUS, CASE WHEN DB_STATUS = 'ACTIVE' THEN '0' WHEN DB_STATUS = 'QUIESCE_PEND' THEN '1' WHEN DB_STATUS = 'QUIESCED' THEN '2' WHEN DB_STATUS = 'ROLLFWD' THEN '3' ELSE '4' END status FROM SYSIBMADM.SNAPDB WHERE DB_NAME='${here/dbsiname}'
